Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is because
Dialogue: 0,00:20:42.25,00:20:45.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何でもできるお前が\N羨ましくって→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was jealous because\Nyou were good at everything.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:45.82,00:20:49.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は勝手に\Nお前を俺のライバルに決めた。
